frege.run7

Class Box<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • frege.run7.Box<R>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Lazy<R>, java.util.concurrent.Callable<R>

    public class Box<R>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Lazy<R>

    Java values and primitives can be put in boxes to make them lazy. This should use less memory than Thunks, and may also avoid auto(un)boxing for primitives.

    The method Thunk#box will create appropriate boxes.
